data.description: Impeccable like new 3-bed, 3.5-bath home, blends rural charm w/city convenience. Enjoy tranquil water views amidst a serene forest, w/the occasional whale sighting. Just mins from ferry, PSNS, & Silverdale shopping. Experience three levels of refined living w/thoughtful upgrades. Open main level features stone fireplace w/custom live edge mantel, modern kitchen w/gas range & deck showing Dyes Inlet & Olympic range. Upstairs, a spacious primary suite promises breathtaking views, spa-like bath & closet organizers. Lower level opens to a patio, w/add'l living space, bed, & bath. Lawn w/irrigation maintained by HOA. Impressive insulated garage w/polyaspartic floor, & tankless WH. Heat pump/A/C for efficiency. Incl. 3yr building defect warranty
